Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.84,0:01:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个土地才是我的王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.02,0:02:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝福奢望野心的国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.29,0:02:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第十九话\N雷太郎的野望\N被禁止王国的幻想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.27,0:02:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊豆真是个不错的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.31,0:02:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好兴奋喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.64,0:02:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能在这种地方好好的玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.15,0:02:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 阿薰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.98,0:02:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等 等一下 不要动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.06,0:02:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小薰小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.29,0:02:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玄斋的妹妹\N应该快来接我们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.86,0:02:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.80,0:02:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎各位来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.00,0:02:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家的事我常听我哥哥提起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.21,0:02:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长得真像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.18,0:02:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.41,0:02:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 小薰小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.65,0:03:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等 等一下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.13,0:03:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要麻烦您照顾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.80,0:03:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经很久没有休假了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.63,0:03:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊豆是个很好的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.87,0:03:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好的玩个一两个礼拜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.44,0:03:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.68,0:03:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩个半个月吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.85,0:03:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了 一个月！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.22,0:03:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的诊疗所没关系吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.65,0:03:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交给玄斋大夫 没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.06,0:03:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的有点兴致勃勃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.86,0:03:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小少爷不知道会是什么脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.56,0:03:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.80,0:03:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在带你们到我家之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.50,0:03:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何想让你们见一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.14,0:04:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎小少爷在需要人照顾时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.04,0:04:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,双亲都去逝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.95,0:04:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五岁的时候 就成为那间房子的主人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.42,0:04:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在五岁的时候？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.95,0:04:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从这里能看到的土地 全部是少爷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.76,0:04:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.35,0:04:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真惊人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.82,0:04:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你一生中都没缘份的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.89,0:04:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.65,0:04:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.36,0:04:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有的东西都是小少爷的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.39,0:04:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请原谅我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.76,0:04:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要我说几次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.96,0:04:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想早一点学剑术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.17,0:05:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要到什么时候才能找到师父呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.04,0:05:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…由太郎小少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.01,0:05:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去给我找来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.17,0:05:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要比死去的父亲还差的剑豪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.91,0:05:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您死去的父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.01,0:05:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被人们称为伊豆的雷神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.38,0:05:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟他的技术相比的师父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.02,0:05:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能找到还是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.99,0:05:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能像父亲一样的师父是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.09,0:05:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要变得跟我父亲一样的强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.06,0:05:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到明天为止给我找来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.90,0:05:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是很拽的小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.88,0:05:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是亲戚吗 好好去玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.81,0:05:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你一直煮好吃的饭菜给我吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.15,0:05:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 这一位就是我常跟你说的剑豪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.16,0:05:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强得会让你吓一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.43,0:06:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长得不是像女孩子一样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.93,0:06:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 如果有相当的技术的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.20,0:06:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上让我见识见识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.81,0:06:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用那把刀 将那吊灯打下来让我看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.45,0:06:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父亲..父亲用被称为雷神的剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.36,0:06:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在15岁的时候 将那吊灯打落下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.83,0:06:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能做同样的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.46,0:06:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就有资格成为我的师父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.63,0:06:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,试看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.87,0:06:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常的不凑巧…..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.44,0:06:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小生并不想成为剑术的师父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.61,0:06:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.71,0:06:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你住其他的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.87,0:06:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并给你佣人使唤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.14,0:06:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是马吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.54,0:06:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想要马吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.58,0:06:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个..我不知道小少爷什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.85,0:06:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经忍不下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.49,0:06:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祢彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.32,0:07:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你再侮辱剑心一句看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.12,0:07:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明神祢彦就不饶你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.19,0:07:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你..你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.56,0:07:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轻视剑心的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.30,0:07:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我无论如何不会原谅他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.50,0:07:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你再等100年 也没有学剑…术的资格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.60,0:07:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你..要对小少爷做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.30,0:07:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.55,0:07:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.92,0:07:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是祢彦所说的事是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.69,0:07:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人的身心皆还未成熟…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.02,0:07:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你对师父也倨傲神气支使人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.09,0:07:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么也学不到…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.66,0:07:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学剑术 就是要从心里开始学起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.07,0:07:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管你的师父是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.10,0:07:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在的你绝对没办法成为强者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.81,0:07:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在对什么人说话….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.14,0:07:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是我的房子！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.81,0:07:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是主人！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.88,0:07:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小少爷 马已经准备好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.68,0:08:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是散步的时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.02,0:08:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出去！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.32,0:08:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用你说…小少爷！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.13,0:08:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙好没水准！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.03,0:08:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？不是跟某位很像吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.31,0:08:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不喜欢认输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.81,0:08:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常的傲慢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.58,0:08:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开 开玩笑！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.64,0:08:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且还有一点尿骚味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.35,0:08:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被大人服侍着长大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.82,0:08:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会那么的傲慢自大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.72,0:08:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心地却是非常正直的少年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.49,0:08:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有好的师父教导他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.86,0:08:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎少爷一定能成为强者的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.16,0:08:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小少爷 危险！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.73,0:08:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住嘴！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.17,0:08:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 第一次被那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.08,0:09:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小..小少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.36,0:09:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不要杀他！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.96,0:09:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有那么大间的房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.39,0:09:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以拿到很多的赎金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.47,0:09:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.57,0:09:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不得了了…小少爷.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.87,0:09:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太无礼了！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.87,0:09:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我是谁吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.64,0:09:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要溜走啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.23,0:09:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死去的父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.43,0:10:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被为雷神的剑术高超者…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.37,0:10:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那支剑如闪电般让这世界裂开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.04,0:10:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如闪电般…闪电般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.95,0:10:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为…什么？为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.76,0:10:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.80,0:10:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.33,0:10:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要无意义的杀生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.04,0:10:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请让我知道你的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.08,0:10:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,石动…雷十太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.61,0:10:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,石动雷十太…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.91,0:10:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是我父亲的再生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.75,0:10:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的师父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.39,0:10:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.57,0:11:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷十太师父\N从现在起要住在这屋子里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.60,0:11:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是少有的剑术高手\N而且是我的恩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.47,0:11:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家不要怠慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.64,0:11:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要跟我父亲一样的尊重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.21,0:11:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可无理 否则我绝不原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.39,0:11:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷太郎师父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.50,0:11:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷太郎师父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.70,0:11:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,师父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.10,0:11:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,师父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.51,0:11:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷十太师父\N什么时候要开始练习呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.28,0:11:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在很想开始练习…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.78,0:11:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要喋喋不休
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.75,0:11:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果想成为强者的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.88,0:11:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.02,0:12:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.09,0:12:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.60,0:12:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑术只有杀人和被杀而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.40,0:12:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竹刀是小孩子的玩具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.01,0:12:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再拿了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.35,0:12:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已经是我辈的孩子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.29,0:12:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经不是小孩子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.36,0:12:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是真古流的四天王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.53,0:12:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真古流？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.80,0:12:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷十太大人的同志…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.24,0:12:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你从现在开始\N是真古流的一员了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.94,0:12:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要以雷十太大人的同志为荣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.65,0:13:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.66,0:13:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.69,0:13:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.19,0:13:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…好快乐喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.26,0:13:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来伊豆还是要洗温泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.73,0:13:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对身体很好还可以消除疲劳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.23,0:13:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 剑哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.27,0:13:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说得好像有去工作一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.34,0:14:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是有去采集草药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.02,0:14:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.45,0:14:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们不可以偷看我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.49,0:14:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会那样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.35,0:14:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要偷看的话\N也要看值得看的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.03,0:14:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.03,0:14:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好期待喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.93,0:14:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 被说成那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.17,0:14:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被这么说反而想去偷看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.04,0:14:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈..想得美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.81,0:14:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有男的在旁边\N你认为我们会脱光光吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.28,0:14:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太狡猾了 太狡猾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.12,0:14:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是哪边狡猾呢…..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.09,0:14:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在做什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.89,0:14:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不快点把衣服晒干就要下山了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.33,0:14:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.23,0:14:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.38,0:15:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那支太刀….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.75,0:15:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来历不明 隐藏在黑暗里的石动雷十太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.35,0:15:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是何人物…..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.39,0:15:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么由太郎从那时候开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.29,0:15:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已完全听雷十太大人的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.16,0:15:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.40,0:15:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一些来历不明的家伙\N也都住进房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.77,0:15:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来历不明的家伙？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.14,0:15:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是年轻的男子\N在大房子绕一圈后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.24,0:15:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连冢山家的传家之宝\N都私自拿出去卖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.08,0:15:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎可这样！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.11,0:15:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用那些钱买了一大堆的刀枪来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.95,0:15:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论什么都是..\N真古流所需要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.89,0:15:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真古流…！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.12,0:15:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.42,0:15:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小薰小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.36,0:15:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎卷进了不寻常的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.63,0:16:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要尽快把由太郎少爷\N从雷十太的身边带走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.60,0:16:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.00,0:16:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先暂时让他住在花婆婆这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.77,0:16:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心 笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.44,0:16:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.87,0:16:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真行 飞天御剑流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.95,0:16:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,守住这个山崖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.72,0:16:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么王国就完成…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.99,0:16:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷十太大人已控制那小鬼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.43,0:16:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是那男的真的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.16,0:16:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,错不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.43,0:16:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的杀人拔刀斋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.74,0:16:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎 我应该有叫你走开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.18,0:16:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.73,0:17:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那支刀不适合由太郎少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.60,0:17:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你都是一个人在练习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.57,0:17:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…雷十太吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.24,0:17:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你连师父的脚都不及还这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.91,0:17:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想跟师父一样的强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.69,0:17:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是特别前来的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.02,0:17:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拔刀斋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.46,0:17:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,师父！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.80,0:17:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我回大屋子去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.23,0:17:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.10,0:17:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有话对你说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.71,0:17:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有话对我说？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.94,0:17:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得这明治时代怎样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.95,0:18:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑术用竹刀来挥着玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.55,0:18:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个时代已经坠落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.58,0:18:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在国民平等之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.09,0:18:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在武士的灵魂已死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.86,0:18:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.70,0:18:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的命\N永远跟这支剑共存着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.40,0:18:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你加入我们的真古流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.40,0:18:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们想借重传说的杀人者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.18,0:18:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们以前都是武士\N以杀人活过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.75,0:18:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明治时期后实施废刀令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.22,0:18:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我们丢掉剑不如叫我们去死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.12,0:18:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时代要我们丢弃我们的骄傲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.19,0:18:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.96,0:18:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们这时候\N能成为一般的市民吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.96,0:18:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样的话….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.36,0:18:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要创造自己的王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.60,0:18:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.13,0:18:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我们这里邀集所有精练剑术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.27,0:18:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并使杀人剑术\N能发挥到极限的人来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.00,0:19:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在伊豆创造出\N最强的集团真古流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.41,0:19:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋….
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.75,0:19:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们准备迎接政府强烈的攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.41,0:19:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时候伊豆的深崖\N会成为我们很好的城壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.55,0:19:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会练就一身\N不畏西洋枪炮的剑术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.99,0:19:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让那洋里洋气的政府知道\N日本古来的武术才是最强的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.76,0:19:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是那会让住在这里\N无辜的百姓牺牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.60,0:19:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也是没办法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.60,0:19:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个国家不是有教我们吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.04,0:19:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强者因为弱者的牺牲\N才能君临天下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.44,0:19:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是\N以杀人剑而生存的拔刀斋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.51,0:19:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用那最强的剑助我们建设王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.35,0:19:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.12,0:19:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.99,0:19:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.32,0:19:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是保护弱小穷苦的民众的剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.29,0:19:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并不是为了一个人\N而建设王国的剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.96,0:19:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们也要觉醒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.93,0:19:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每个人考虑该怎么生存下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.93,0:19:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡扯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.13,0:20:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不战斗的话我们的人生也完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.04,0:20:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀人者应该忘记你的存在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.34,0:20:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拔刀斋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.71,0:20:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们不觉醒的话 小生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.58,0:20:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打算不杀你们\N而把你们给消灭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.39,0:20:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样..\N你已知道所有的密秘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.23,0:20:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.04,0:20:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从全国各地所挑选出来的好手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.75,0:20:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的同志真古流四天王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.25,0:20:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使是拔刀斋也没办法赢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.46,0:21:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好..好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.94,0:21:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.38,0:21:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.89,0:21:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要能封闭你的神速\N你也会没有办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.26,0:21:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧 拔刀斋
